snippet.title: Valkyria Chronicles Duel - My Gameplay 01
snippet.description:
An awesome game made to be played using a browser: Valkyria Chronicles Duel.
Based off of the legendary Valkyria Chronicles series of: Valkryia Chronicles(PS3), Valkyria Chronicles 2(PSP), Valkryia Chronicles 3/Extra Edition(PSP)!

Valkyria Chronicles Duel PV:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWZB9atiQ1w

Valkyria Chronicles Duel Official Website:
http://valkyria-duel.hangame.co.jp/index.nhn

A walkthrough on how to get started to play:
http://aliciasbakery.blogspot.com.au/2012/06/visual-walkthrough-for-valkyria-duel.html

An english video tutorial on how to play the game:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i0gESAe9s5s

A short gameplay video of Valkyria Chronicles Duel:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tYIrGMjG9Zo&feature=youtu.be

A work-in-progress Wikipedia for Valkyria Chronicles Duel:
http://valkyria.wikia.com/wiki/Valkyria_Chronicles_Duel

Special thanks to the Gallian Liberation Front:
http://www.facebook.com/GLFront

Other Info:
http://andriasang.com/con1zq/valkyria_browser/
